room_title: Escape room "The Gauntlet" by Esc4pe Room in Burlington
room_description: Welcome to P.I.T.O.N. Here we have eyes everywhere, including on you. In the Gauntlet, you and 3-7 allies will have the chance to prove your skills at encryption, intelligence gathering, and creative thinking. If you can pass our tests and complete your mission before time runs out, you will prove yourselves to be perfect spy material.
